unpublishedAction.name: initializeRetainKPObject

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
        const retain_keyPersonData = {}
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ENTITY_TYPE = 'Key Person Foreign'
				retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TYPE = vayKeyPersonFgnType.selectedOptionValue
				//showAlert('Key Person Tyep'+ retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TYPE)
			  retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_IS_AUTH_SIGN = Checkbox1.isChecked
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_OTHERS_INFO = Input2.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PARTNER_PERC = Input18.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FIRSTNAME = Input1.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MIDDLENAME = Input3.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_LASTNAME = Input4.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOTHERNAME = Input5.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_FATHERNAME = Input6.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DOB = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_TAX_ID = Input7.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_NATIONALITY = Select3.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_RES_TAX_PURPOSE = Select4.selectedOptionValue
        //retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DESIGNATION  = ''
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_NO = Input21.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_PASSPORT_EXPIRE_DATE = moment(DatePicker1).format("YYYY-MM-DD")
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ACCESS_AS = vayKeyPersonFgnUserAccess.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_DIN_DPIN = Input8.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE1 = Input9.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_LINE2 = Input10.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY = Input11.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_DISTRICT = Input12.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE = Input.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY = vayFgnKeyPersonAddCountrySelec.selectedOptionValue
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_ADDRESS_ZIP = Input15.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_MOBILE = Input16.text
        retain_keyPersonData.CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_EMAIL = Input17.text
        appsmith.store.vayCCY.map((item) => {
            return ({
                CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_CODE_FORADMTXN: item,
                CUSTOMER_KEY_PERSON_CURRENCY_LIMIT: Input19.text
            });
        });
        return retain_keyPersonData
    }
